<section class="section">
  <h2>Our Story</h2>
  <p>A_team_Recruiter was founded with a single mission — to bridge the gap between skilled professionals and businesses in need of quality talent. We began as a small team with big ideas and a deep belief in the power of the right hire.</p>

  <p>Over the years, we've partnered with startups, SMEs, and large enterprises to help them meet critical hiring demands across IT and Non-IT sectors. Today, we’re proud to be one of the fastest-growing recruitment consultancies offering tailored solutions, quick TATs, and a deep candidate network across India.</p>

  <h2>Our Mission</h2>
  <p>To connect organizations with top-tier talent through a transparent, effective, and value-driven recruitment process.</p>

  <h2>Our Vision</h2>
  <p>To be recognized as a trusted recruitment partner by consistently delivering the right people to power the future of businesses.</p>

  <h2>Core Values</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Integrity and Transparency</li>
    <li>Speed with Quality</li>
    <li>Client-first Approach</li>
    <li>Candidate Empowerment</li>
    <li>Long-term Partnerships</li>
  </ul>
